        <remarks>
          <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-115">此屬性取得並設定 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReliableSessionBindingElement.InactivityTimeout%2A> 屬性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-115">The property gets and sets the value of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReliableSessionBindingElement.InactivityTimeout%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-116">通道上的活動定義為收到應用程式或基礎結構訊息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-116">Activity on a channel is defined as receiving an application or infrastructure message.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-117">無活動逾時會控制讓非作用中工作階段保持運作的最大時間量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-117">The inactivity timeout property controls the maximum amount of time to keep an inactive session alive.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-118">如果超過 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableSession.InactivityTimeout%2A> 指定時間間隔沒有任何活動，基礎結構和通道錯誤便會中止工作階段，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-118">If more than the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableSession.InactivityTimeout%2A> specified time interval passes with no activity, the session is aborted by the infrastructure and the channel faults.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-119">此時可靠工作階段會單方面遭到終止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-119">The reliable session is torn down unilaterally.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-120">如果傳送應用程式沒有訊息要傳送，則可靠工作階段通常不會因無活動而發生錯誤；相反地，保持作用中的機制會無限期地讓工作階段保持在作用中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-120">If the sending application has no messages to send then the reliable session is normally not faulted because of inactivity; instead a keep-alive mechanism keeps the session active indefinitely.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-121">請注意，如果沒有傳送或接收應用程式訊息，發送器可以獨立中止可靠工作階段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-121">Note that the dispatcher could independently abort the reliable session if no application messages are sent or received.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-122">因此，如果網路狀況造成沒有收到任何訊息，或是如果傳送者有失敗，無活動逾時通常就會過期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-122">Thus, the inactivity timeout typically expires if network conditions are such that no messages of any sort are received or if there is a failure on the sender.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-123">設定此逾時可避免用戶端未關閉安全性階段時，伺服器緊抓住它不放。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-123">Setting this timeout prevents the server from holding onto a security session if the client does not close it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-124">若安全性工作階段在一段無活動時間間隔內未接收到訊息，它就會被伺服器關閉。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-124">If the security session has not received a message for the inactivity interval of time, it is closed by the server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-125">如此可降低阻絕服務攻擊的潛在可能性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-125">This mitigates a potential denial of service attack.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-126">使用可靠工作階段時，必須滿足兩個不同的無活動計時器，才能保持連線運作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-126">When using a reliable session, there are two different inactivity timers that must be satisfied to keep the connection alive.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-127">如果其中一個無活動計時器引發，就會中斷連線。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-127">If either of these inactivity timers goes off, then the connection is dropped.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-128">第一個無活動計時器在可靠的工作階段，稱為 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableSession.InactivityTimeout%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-128">The first inactivity timer is on the reliable session and is called the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableSession.InactivityTimeout%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-129">如果在逾時期限內未收到訊息 (應用程式或基礎結構訊息)，便會引發這個無活動計時器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-129">This inactivity timer fires if no messages, either application or infrastructure, are received within the timeout period.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-130">基礎結構訊息是為了通道堆疊的其中一個通訊協定 (例如保持運作或通知) 所產生的訊息，而非包含應用程式資料的訊息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-130">An infrastructure message is a message that is generated for the purpose of one of the protocols in the channel stack, such as a keep alive or an acknowledgment, rather than containing application data.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-131">第二個無活動計時器位於服務上，會使用繫結的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.ReceiveTimeout%2A> 設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-131">The second inactivity timer is on the service and uses the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.ReceiveTimeout%2A> setting of the binding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-132">如果在逾時期限內未收到應用程式訊息，便會引發這個無活動計時器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-132">This inactivity timer fires if no application messages are received within the timeout period.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-133">因為其中一個無活動計時器引發便會中斷連線，因此當 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableSession.InactivityTimeout%2A> 大於 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.ReceiveTimeout%2A> 時增加前者沒有任何作用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-133">Since the connection is dropped if either inactivity timer fires, increasing <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableSession.InactivityTimeout%2A> once it is greater than <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding.ReceiveTimeout%2A> has no effect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7c5a-134">這兩個計時器的預設逾時都是 10 分鐘，因此在使用可靠工作階段時，一定要同時增加兩者，才會有所差別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7c5a-134">The default for both of these timeouts is 10 minutes, so you always have to increase both of them to make a difference when using a reliable session.</span></span>  
  
   
  
